{"tid":1477053,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（尋人）搵一個住係深水埗而老母又係機場返工既巴","createTime":"2019-08-16T04:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T03:28:58.000Z","uid":148524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"acf7938422a203cec9f66e967defc735f801c320","tid":1477053,"uid":148524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:13:36.000Z","msg":"尋日我係機場同你媽媽講左少少近日既事 發現佢好多野都唔清楚 唔了解 佢仲話黑警唔會亂打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊研究下點樣可以改變你媽媽既想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老母特徵：<br />\n-工作時帶口罩<br />\n-係機場外返工既 （好似係藍色制服 + 反光衣）<br />\n-住深水埗狗屋附近<br />\n-訓教發夢疑似夢到特朗普老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-14號單拖出直席深水埗燒街衣活動，直至凌晨一 兩點先回家 （有同你講 叫你唔好擔心）<br />\n-你有同媽媽講過「你有冇為香港做過d咩？遊行，示威 你都冇去」之類既說話<br />\n<br />\n自己老母自己救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90127574aeb42d27401abf698b2016695d970143","tid":1477053,"uid":148524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:15:13.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9da6e3456293cb98020abdbcc46d4cdf8f020d","tid":1477053,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:23:10.000Z","msg":"人地老母關你撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd52928b20e5190b9f79ef1587c5ecd8709a5a4","tid":1477053,"uid":148524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb9da6e3456293cb98020abdbcc46d4cdf8f020d","tid":1477053,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:23:10.000Z","msg":"人地老母關你撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:47:22.000Z","msg":"幫得一個得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01179cb1684de9e9868f8b5cbd8e81e1f38d4926","tid":1477053,"uid":148524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,